title: Hindī-śabdasāgara, arthāt, Hindī bhāshā kā eka br̥hat kośa / sampādaka, Śyāmasundaradāsa ; sahāyaka sampādaka Bālakr̥shṇa Bhaṭṭa ... [et al.]
